    "en": {
      "title": "The 12th Beijing International Film Festival begins",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Shen Haixiong, Chairman of China Media Group (CMG) and Chairman of the 12th BJIFF Organizing Committee, gave a speech and announced the opening of the Beijing International Film Festival.",
        "Mao Gaoi, a member of the Standing Committee of the Beijing Municipal Committee of the Communist Party of China (CPC) and Director General of the Propaganda Department of the CPC Beijing Municipal Committee, also attended the event and delivered a speech."
